A CameraNode going offline means EVERY camera attached to it has
also gone dark. Cameras will appear offline in the dashboard
until the node reconnects.

What this might mean:
  - The host machine crashed, lost power, or was rebooted.
  - The systemd service / Windows Service stopped (check the host).
  - The host lost internet connectivity entirely.

Open the admin panel: {{ dashboard_url }}/admin

